00:26:36,009 --> 00:26:37,679
So? It's just an AE86.

268
00:28:07,425 --> 00:28:07,995
You OK?

269
00:28:24,842 --> 00:28:27,758
I forgot to tell you. This is just a tofu delivery car.

270
00:28:27,759 --> 00:28:29,719
You can't race us in this.

271
00:28:29,884 --> 00:28:31,854
You could get hurt, got it?

272
00:28:35,300 --> 00:28:38,570
That's right. You guys are professional racers.

273
00:28:39,092 --> 00:28:42,232
Of course you look down on us street racers.

274
00:28:42,550 --> 00:28:46,520
Professional or street doesn't matter.
We're all racers.

275
00:28:47,217 --> 00:28:49,827
Right, you beat me once, didn't you?

276
00:28:52,050 --> 00:28:52,980
You remember?

277
00:28:53,550 --> 00:28:54,710
Wanna win again?

278
00:28:55,050 --> 00:28:58,010
