285
00:29:57,134 --> 00:29:58,884
Just talking, no hitting.

286
00:29:59,467 --> 00:30:03,487
Hitting your kid in public will be very traumatic to him.

287
00:30:05,384 --> 00:30:06,534
I'm going home.

288
00:30:33,009 --> 00:30:35,339
Are you still upset about losing?

289
00:30:37,175 --> 00:30:39,383
I challenged Kyouichi, the guy who beat you,

290
00:30:39,384 --> 00:30:40,994
to a race in 3 weeks.

291
00:30:42,884 --> 00:30:43,984
You're invited.

292
00:30:45,759 --> 00:30:48,419
If you don't have another car, I do.

293
00:30:51,592 --> 00:30:54,612
Thanks, but I only wanna drive my own car.

294
00:30:55,759 --> 00:30:58,079
Call me if you change your mind.

295
00:31:23,342 --> 00:31:25,912
Want some cheesecake? It's delicious!

296
00:31:28,800 --> 00:31:30,720
Natsuki brought it for you.

297
00:31:31,675 --> 00:31:33,005
When was she here?

298
00:31:37,175 --> 00:31:41,995
She's going away for a couple of weeks,
but she'll call you later.

299
00:31:44,925 --> 00:31:46,545
What else did she say?

300
00:31:50,092 --> 00:31:52,832
Was she supposed to say something else?

301
00:32:00,842 --> 00:32:01,592
Hey! Hey!!

302
00:32:03,425 --> 00:32:05,299
You're gonna eat the whole cake??

303
00:32:05,300 --> 00:32:07,510
You'll stuff yourself to death!

304
00:33:11,092 --> 00:33:13,952
Tofuman, your AE86 is already an antique.

305
00:33:15,259 --> 00:33:18,619
Might as well switch to a new car. Why fix it?

306
00:33:19,717 --> 00:33:22,508
Don't tell me you gonna put THAT
into the AE86?!

307
00:33:22,509 --> 00:33:24,009
Isn't this a beauty?

308
00:33:27,009 --> 00:33:30,899
