You wanna go to jail?!

309
00:33:33,675 --> 00:33:34,595
You're nuts.

310
00:34:00,717 --> 00:34:02,417
Catching roaches, Itsuki?

311
00:34:03,259 --> 00:34:04,924
No, looking for my old man.

312
00:34:04,925 --> 00:34:07,549
He's been gone for days, just like you.

313
00:34:07,550 --> 00:34:08,190
Customer.

314
00:34:09,675 --> 00:34:12,175
That sucks. He's not young anymore.

315
00:34:12,259 --> 00:34:15,216
He can't just leave his business like this.
That's irresponsible!

316
00:34:15,217 --> 00:34:17,508
