321
00:34:46,842 --> 00:34:49,332
We went for a spin at Mount Akina.

322
00:35:52,134 --> 00:35:53,284
Is he down yet?

323
00:35:53,925 --> 00:35:54,445
Coming.

324
00:36:03,967 --> 00:36:05,707
