326
00:37:01,009 --> 00:37:01,579
Hop in.

327
00:37:11,925 --> 00:37:13,466
I’ll only show you once.

328
00:37:13,467 --> 00:37:17,097
Watch carefully. Pay attention to the new tachometer.

329
00:37:21,550 --> 00:37:22,716
Its power won't become obvious

330
00:37:22,717 --> 00:37:24,857
until it's above 11,000 revs.

331
00:37:55,342 --> 00:37:57,612
Sit tight. I wanna drive faster.

332
00:38:16,259 --> 00:38:16,779
Miya...

333
00:38:18,634 --> 00:38:21,324
That Kaiseki dinner was delicious, huh?

334
00:38:21,884 --> 00:38:22,514
Not bad.

335
00:38:23,425 --> 00:38:24,345
That's good.

336
00:38:24,967 --> 00:38:26,966
Thanks so much for taking care of me

337
00:38:26,967 --> 00:38:29,508
while I puked for two days straight.

338
00:38:29,509 --> 00:38:32,179
You were like a goddess who saved me.

339
00:38:36,384 --> 00:38:37,304
You're nuts.

340
00:38:37,592 --> 00:38:38,512
I'm serious.

341
00:38:39,300 --> 00:38:40,630
I believe in gods.

342
00:38:41,842 --> 00:38:43,282
A god is human too,

343
00:38:43,717 --> 00:38:46,716
but he can do things other humans can't do.

344
00:38:46,717 --> 00:38:48,437
That's why he's a god.

345
00:38:49,384 --> 00:38:50,884
But do you know that

346
00:38:51,592 --> 00:38:54,782
a god also have the same urges as us humans?

347
00:38:58,550 --> 00:39:00,424
What're you trying to say?

348
00:39:00,425 --> 00:39:01,825
Most humans would...

349
00:39:03,009 --> 00:39:04,109
sometimes go to

350
00:39:06,634 --> 00:39:08,204
this love hotel and...

351
00:39:08,717 --> 00:39:10,424
Since you're also in the "fill it up" business,

352
00:39:10,425 --> 00:39:12,925
Miya, I'm sure you wouldn’t mind...

353
00:39:17,009 --> 00:39:17,589
Pervert!

354
00:39:31,342 --> 00:39:31,982
Natsuki?!

355
00:39:45,884 --> 00:39:47,044
What the hell..?

356
00:39:49,134 --> 00:39:51,634
I test-drove with my dad yesterday.

357
00:39:51,717 --> 00:39:54,327
Turns out it's got a new tachometer.

358
00:39:54,342 --> 00:39:56,049
I just found out yesterday.

359
00:39:56,050 --> 00:39:58,100
Imagine. AE86, 250 horsepower.

360
00:40:00,842 --> 00:40:02,922
You know how fast is 250 hp?

361
00:40:03,634 --> 00:40:05,784
I did Mount Akina at 150kph...

362
00:40:08,092 --> 00:40:10,924
It only took me a little more than 3 minutes.

363
00:40:10,925 --> 00:40:11,855
Amazing, huh?

364
00:40:14,342 --> 00:40:16,852
I really wanna tell everyone. You...

365
00:40:18,592 --> 00:40:19,462
and Natsuki.

366
00:40:22,759 --> 00:40:23,389
No need.

367
00:40:24,259 --> 00:40:25,529
No need for what?

368
00:40:26,467 --> 00:40:28,207
No need to tell Natsuki.

369
00:40:32,634 --> 00:40:33,154
Takumi.

370
00:40:35,384 --> 00:40:38,994
There's something I... I wanna tell my best friend.

371
00:40:39,175 --> 00:40:40,035
Who's that?

372
00:40:40,884 --> 00:40:41,224
You.

373
00:40:42,175 --> 00:40:42,865
Go ahead.

374
00:40:49,509 --> 00:40:50,669
I saw Natsuki...

375
00:40:53,842 --> 00:40:56,392
Going into a love hotel with a guy.

376
00:40:58,134 --> 00:41:00,004
--Love hotel? --Love hotel.

377
00:41:00,342 --> 00:41:01,322
Are you sure?

378
00:41:04,384 --> 00:41:07,104
It only costs 30,000 yen to bang her.

379
00:41:10,342 --> 00:41:11,612
What did you say?

380
00:41:15,425 --> 00:41:17,155
30,000 yen to bang her!

381
00:41:17,759 --> 00:41:19,379
Your girl is a hooker!

382
00:41:23,259 --> 00:41:24,924
What're you talking about??

383
00:41:24,925 --> 00:41:26,966
I'm trying to help you and you hit me?!

384
00:41:26,967 --> 00:41:27,827
Go to hell!

385
00:41:28,425 --> 00:41:32,245
I've known you since 7 and you hit me over a whore??

386
00:41:34,092 --> 00:41:34,602
Don't!

387
00:41:46,675 --> 00:41:47,305
Stop it!

388
00:41:47,884 --> 00:41:48,864
Come, hit me!

389
00:41:51,050 --> 00:41:52,320
Go ahead, hit me!

390
00:41:56,884 --> 00:41:58,044
Takumi, stop it!

391
00:41:59,175 --> 00:42:00,035
Let's talk!

392
00:42:00,300 --> 00:42:01,230
Why fighting?

393
00:42:05,592 --> 00:42:06,632
Pull him back!

394
00:42:09,092 --> 00:42:10,072
Stop it, boy!

395
00:42:12,217 --> 00:42:13,327
Stop fighting...

396
00:42:16,134 --> 00:42:16,654
Takumi!

397
00:42:20,384 --> 00:42:22,049
Why did you hit him, you jerk?!

398
00:42:22,050 --> 00:42:25,170
That's right, I'm a jerk! I jerk off too!!

399
00:43:06,175 --> 00:43:07,325
Hello? It's me.

400
00:43:08,300 --> 00:43:12,140
I shouldn’t have called your girl a whore.
I'm sorry.

401
00:43:30,050 --> 00:43:32,440
Did you forget? Today is Saturday.

402
00:43:32,800 --> 00:43:35,770
Everyone is waiting for you and your AE86.

403
00:44:50,675 --> 00:44:51,135
Hello.

404
00:44:51,425 --> 00:44:51,885
Hello?

405
00:44:52,092 --> 00:44:52,772
It's me.

406
00:44:53,384 --> 00:44:54,184
What's up?

407
00:44:54,467 --> 00:44:56,008
I've been looking for you.

408
00:44:56,009 --> 00:44:57,859
I've been in my hometown.

409
00:44:58,300 --> 00:45:01,840
I'm boarding the train now. I'll be back tonight.

410
00:45:01,967 --> 00:45:04,383
I'm racing at Mount Akina tonight.

411
00:45:04,384 --> 00:45:06,383
I'll come see you right after the race, OK?

412
00:45:06,384 --> 00:45:09,591
No...Why don't I come see you tomorrow instead?

413
00:45:09,592 --> 00:45:11,216
The train is here. Talk to you later.

414
00:45:11,217 --> 00:45:13,487
Natsuki, I really wanna see you.

415
00:45:18,425 --> 00:45:19,005
Natsuki.

416
00:45:20,342 --> 00:45:24,542
I've really enjoyed your company
this past 2 weeks, thanks.

417
00:45:25,384 --> 00:45:28,114
Did I give you enough money last time?

418
00:45:30,592 --> 00:45:34,602
It's better that we don't see each other
after tonight.

419
00:45:39,217 --> 00:45:41,767
I don't wanna be like this anymore.

420
00:45:42,884 --> 00:45:47,354
I don't wanna see you again.
I want to forget about all this.

421
00:45:48,009 --> 00:45:50,669
All I want now is to be with Takumi.

422
00:46:11,217 --> 00:46:13,549
Isn't it a bit too much, broomhead?

423
00:46:13,550 --> 00:46:15,060
I know Ryousuke well.

424
00:46:17,592 --> 00:46:20,202
I will never lose to the same guy...

425
00:46:22,092 --> 00:46:22,552
twice.

426
00:46:29,217 --> 00:46:32,107
Shit, I hope I didn't hurt him too bad.

427
00:46:34,217 --> 00:46:35,377
You should talk.

428
00:46:37,967 --> 00:46:40,587
Your nose has been bleeding for days.

429
00:46:41,842 --> 00:46:43,582
See? There you go again.

430
00:46:46,342 --> 00:46:49,902
Will this become a monthly thing
like your period?

431
00:46:55,509 --> 00:46:58,216
What're we waiting for?? Everyone's here!

432
00:46:58,217 --> 00:46:59,427
What's the rush?

433
00:46:59,800 --> 00:47:01,590
I'll give him 5 minutes.

434
00:47:01,759 --> 00:47:06,419
Doesn't really matter if he comes.
Tonight is between you and me.

435
00:47:11,842 --> 00:47:15,299
Block the road. The race will begin in 5 minutes.

436
00:47:15,300 --> 00:47:16,920
Wait! A car is coming!

437
00:47:28,259 --> 00:47:29,349
It's the AE86!

438
00:47:38,425 --> 00:47:42,008
We never had so many girls at our races back then!

439
00:47:42,009 --> 00:47:42,989
That's right.

440
00:47:43,175 --> 00:47:46,485
This is a ladies-only zone, pops. Take a hike.

441
00:47:57,384 --> 00:47:58,304
It's coming!

442
00:48:14,675 --> 00:48:17,585
So you've resurrected this piece of junk?

443
00:48:17,884 --> 00:48:19,384
Way to go, tofu boy!

444
00:48:20,592 --> 00:48:23,612
And where's your car, the one you crashed?

445
00:48:24,009 --> 00:48:26,099
Tofu boy, you wanna go first?

446
00:48:27,259 --> 00:48:30,919
No need. Just drive fast. I got other things to do.

447
00:48:33,384 --> 00:48:34,134
Wear this.

448
00:48:34,800 --> 00:48:35,430
No need.

449
00:48:36,467 --> 00:48:38,841
Ryousuke's got something to tell you.

450
00:48:38,842 --> 00:48:41,772
Listen, Takumi. Kyouichi is a professional,

451
00:48:42,467 --> 00:48:44,591
but all professionals have their weaknesses...

452
00:48:44,592 --> 00:48:47,299
You don't need to teach me. I'm gonna beat him.

453
00:48:47,300 --> 00:48:48,340
What about me?

454
00:48:48,384 --> 00:48:49,764
I'll beat you too.

455
00:49:29,592 --> 00:49:32,782
The road is clear. We can start at any time.

456
00:49:33,009 --> 00:49:35,389
Repeat: We can start at any time.

457
00:49:37,550 --> 00:49:37,770
5!

458
00:49:38,634 --> 00:49:38,854
4!

459
00:49:39,675 --> 00:49:39,895
3!

460
00:49:40,759 --> 00:49:40,979
2!

461
00:49:41,842 --> 00:49:42,062
1!

462
00:49:42,967 --> 00:49:43,307
GO!!

463
00:49:55,884 --> 00:49:57,008
All three cars took off at top speed.

464
00:49:57,009 --> 00:49:58,133
Kyouichi's E3 is leading,

465
00:49:58,134 --> 00:49:59,341
followed by Ryousuke's FC.

466
00:49:59,342 --> 00:50:00,612
The AE86 is last.

467
00:50:16,592 --> 00:50:17,758
They've past the first corner.

468
00:50:17,759 --> 00:50:20,216
Both Ryousuke and Takumi made their best
lap time.

469
00:50:20,217 --> 00:50:23,357
Everyone's faster when they're racing a pro.

470
00:50:46,884 --> 00:50:48,274
What are you doing?

471
00:50:48,342 --> 00:50:49,799
This is called "strategy".

472
00:50:49,800 --> 00:50:51,383
The FC suddenly lags behind right before the tunnel.

473
00:50:51,384 --> 00:50:53,884
I wonder what Ryousuke had in mind?

474
00:51:24,217 --> 00:51:25,216
The speed is unbelievable!

475
00:51:25,217 --> 00:51:27,049
All three cars exceeded 100 kph at the corner just now!

476
00:51:27,050 --> 00:51:28,133
The AE86 is waiting for a chance

477
00:51:28,134 --> 00:51:30,091
to overtake the E3 at the next corner.

478
00:51:30,092 --> 00:51:31,542
Step on it, Takumi!!

479
00:51:32,259 --> 00:51:33,716
Give it back! What's wrong with you??

480
00:51:33,717 --> 00:51:36,557
What's wrong with YOU?? This is a race!

481
00:51:36,884 --> 00:51:38,794
You gotta yell at a race!!

482
00:52:08,134 --> 00:52:08,994
This is it.

483
00:52:21,967 --> 00:52:23,008
They overtook him!

484
00:52:23,009 --> 00:52:24,174
The E3 has hardly any room and

485
00:52:24,175 --> 00:52:25,674
both the FC and AE86 used the ditch

486
00:52:25,675 --> 00:52:26,633
to overtake the E3!

487
00:52:26,634 --> 00:52:28,614
Let me explain, little girl.

488
00:52:28,800 --> 00:52:31,716
In street racing, a professional’s common weakness

489
00:52:31,717 --> 00:52:34,383
is to leave some open space when taking a right corner.

490
00:52:34,384 --> 00:52:35,774
Step on it, Takumi!

491
00:52:41,175 --> 00:52:42,758
Takumi, it's just you and me now.

492
00:52:42,759 --> 00:52:43,966
What about the E3?

493
00:52:43,967 --> 00:52:45,174
I'll block it for you.

494
00:52:45,175 --> 00:52:47,035
Better watch your own ass.

495
00:53:00,009 --> 00:53:02,008
The AE86 and FC both managed to pass a pro!

496
00:53:02,009 --> 00:53:03,469
Who could’ve thought?

497
00:53:03,925 --> 00:53:05,674
But the E3 is not out of it yet!

498
00:53:05,675 --> 00:53:07,133
Although they use different tactics,

499
00:53:07,134 --> 00:53:08,883
the FC and AE86 are way too fast

500
00:53:08,884 --> 00:53:10,394
in the corner drifts.

501
00:53:10,425 --> 00:53:13,095
Catching up to them will not be easy.

502
00:53:21,634 --> 00:53:23,024
Step on it, Takumi!

503
00:54:13,634 --> 00:54:14,984
Attention, everyone!

504
00:54:15,384 --> 00:54:17,799
A vehicle has just left the national park

505
00:54:17,800 --> 00:54:19,174
and it's heading up the mountain!

506
00:54:19,175 --> 00:54:22,895
A car is coming towards you. Get ready to slow down!

507
00:54:26,967 --> 00:54:30,997
Kyouichi is ignoring the warning! He's trying to overtake!

508
00:54:35,967 --> 00:54:37,417
Should we block him?

509
00:54:37,884 --> 00:54:38,574
Too late.

510
00:55:00,842 --> 00:55:02,924
The E3 has crashed! The E3 has crashed!

511
00:55:02,925 --> 00:55:06,091
The AE86 and FC passed through. They're still racing!

512
00:55:06,092 --> 00:55:06,832
Is he OK?

513
00:55:07,175 --> 00:55:07,985
Forget him.

514
00:55:12,342 --> 00:55:13,912
Kyouichi! Are you OK??

515
00:55:44,800 --> 00:55:46,008
They're at the 5 consecutive hairpins.

516
00:55:46,009 --> 00:55:47,569
Can the FC pass here?

517
00:56:09,842 --> 00:56:11,508
"The AE86 is at its Limits.

518
00:56:11,509 --> 00:56:12,889
Now it's my turn."

519
00:56:21,550 --> 00:56:23,410
The FC overtakes the AE86!

520
00:56:23,509 --> 00:56:24,591
There's only 1km left!

521
00:56:24,592 --> 00:56:25,966
I don't think the AE86 can make it.

522
00:56:25,967 --> 00:56:27,067
What the hell?!

523
00:56:27,550 --> 00:56:28,350
I knew it.

524
00:56:29,217 --> 00:56:30,049
You knew what??

525
00:56:30,050 --> 00:56:32,790
Takumi has never taken the lead before.

526
00:56:32,967 --> 00:56:35,966
Ryousuke's car is powerful, but he still
stayed behind Takumi

527
00:56:35,967 --> 00:56:40,047
because he wants to learn his moves and then overtake him.

528
00:56:40,092 --> 00:56:41,508
So it's over for Takumi?

529
00:56:41,509 --> 00:56:42,619
Not necessarily.

530
00:56:54,884 --> 00:56:58,008
You've been driving by yourself all these years.

531
00:56:58,009 --> 00:57:00,216
You've never competed with anyone.

532
00:57:00,217 --> 00:57:00,857
Remember.

533
00:57:02,717 --> 00:57:05,927
Don't pay attention to the competition itself.

534
00:57:06,842 --> 00:57:08,242
Ignore other racers.

535
00:57:09,509 --> 00:57:12,179
The one you need to beat is yourself.

536
00:57:21,300 --> 00:57:23,883
They're almost at the finish line and the
AE86 hasn't given up yet!

537
00:57:23,884 --> 00:57:26,144
It's still right behind the FC.

538
00:57:36,092 --> 00:57:38,299
The FC missed its lane going into the corner!

539
00:57:38,300 --> 00:57:40,633
Can Ryousuke withstand the pressure from the AE86?

540
00:57:40,634 --> 00:57:42,549
The "pressure" comes from the tires.

541
00:57:42,550 --> 00:57:44,508
Even though the car is retuned to 250 hp,

542
00:57:44,509 --> 00:57:46,599
the FC is still too powerful.

543
00:57:46,634 --> 00:57:49,549
But as time drags on, the tires won't hold up,

544
00:57:49,550 --> 00:57:51,508
and the car can't drift all the way.

545
00:57:51,509 --> 00:57:55,749
That's why the last 2 corners are the most
crucial of all!

546
00:57:56,092 --> 00:57:57,252
There they come!

547
00:58:31,925 --> 00:58:33,049
They're almost at the finish line!

548
00:58:33,050 --> 00:58:34,966
The mighty FC still has the edge.

549
00:58:34,967 --> 00:58:37,237
Looks like the outcome is clear.

550
00:58:50,217 --> 00:58:52,717
The FC slows going into the corner!

551
00:58:52,759 --> 00:58:56,429
The AE86 is taking the inner lane.
Can it overtake?

552
00:59:11,467 --> 00:59:12,591
The AE86 has won!!

553
00:59:12,592 --> 00:59:16,202
The AE86 is the ultimate
racing god of Mount Akina!

554
00:59:25,884 --> 00:59:27,564
All right!! He did it!!

555
00:59:38,467 --> 00:59:39,097
He won!!

556
01:00:03,967 --> 01:00:04,767
I've lost.

557
01:00:10,675 --> 01:00:12,415
So, what now? Any plans?

558
01:00:13,134 --> 01:00:14,824
Nothing. What about you?

559
01:00:14,967 --> 01:00:18,797
I'm gonna set up a new race team.
Are you interested?

560
01:00:21,717 --> 01:00:22,877
Dunno. Gotta go.

561
01:00:23,384 --> 01:00:26,054
Takumi! I really want you on my team.

562
01:00:27,425 --> 01:00:28,345
Sleep on it.

563
01:00:31,509 --> 01:00:32,309
We'll see.

564
01:02:01,634 --> 01:02:02,154
Takumi!

565
01:02:07,217 --> 01:02:08,327
Takumi! Takumi!

566
01:03:06,800 --> 01:03:10,799
"The most important thing is
to find a world to belong to."

567
01:03:10,800 --> 01:03:14,300
"Only then will we realize that life is meaningful."

568
01:03:15,175 --> 01:03:18,615
"Takumi... I think for you, that world is racing."

569
01:04:15,009 --> 01:04:16,399
Well? Did you lose?

570
01:04:16,842 --> 01:04:17,532
Hey. Hey!

571
01:04:18,384 --> 01:04:19,824
Let's have a drink!

572
01:04:42,675 --> 01:04:43,825
Son of a bitch.

573
01:04:44,925 --> 01:04:46,255
Itsuki, I'm sorry.

574
01:04:56,425 --> 01:04:58,635
Hey, Ryousuke. It's me, Takumi.

575
01:05:01,884 --> 01:05:02,224
I...

576
01:05:03,717 --> 01:05:05,677
I want to be on your team.

